query: SELECT rm.lojaId, l.nome as lojaNome, rm.taxaReparacao, rm.totalServicos FROM resultados_mensais rm INNER JOIN lojas l ON rm.lojaId = l.id WHERE rm.mes = 1 AND rm.ano = 2026 AND rm.taxaReparacao IS NOT NULL ORDER BY rm.taxaReparacao DESC LIMIT 5;
